# Trained artifacts are regenerated by `python -m src.train` (locally, in CI,
# in the Docker build, and on first request in the deployed app). Keeping them
# out of git avoids scikit-learn version-mismatch issues across environments.
models/*.joblib
models/metrics.json
models/model_card.md

